The use of Gaussian Processes and probabilistic modeling indicates that it may also belong to the cs.LG (Machine Learning) category. The paper involves knowledge transfer between classes, which is a common topic in the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) category. The use of embeddings and representation learning suggests that it may also belong to the cs.MM (Multimedia) category. Finally, the paper involves natural language processing techniques such as self-assessment, which suggests that it may also belong to the cs.CL (Computation and Language) category.
